{
  "stem": "4361.6",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You could see the eyes were blurry and gone.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And eventually, they were just taken.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, we are probably the end of December 1944.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Again, there is something in the air that the war doesn't go the way expected.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this is why it was this attitude, what can you do to me?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Go and sue me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So you'll send me to the crematoria.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You'll do me a favor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What happened was they began to take people-- women, I'm talking only about women because it was a women's camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And some of the transports we heard were marched to death.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were the death marches.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Other transports were put in trains and then blown up somewhere.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, nobody knew what was really happening.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't have shoes by this time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I secured some sort of a wooden [GERMAN], they used to call it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my feet, first of all, it was cutting into the flesh, and they were falling off.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was worse with the shoes on than without.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I remembered I had literally dreams of gigantic shoes, padded, soft, night after night.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was really a misery.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I couldn't stand it anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then, there came a day when they said that they are looking for workers in some factory somewhere.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Again, nobody tells you where, what.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What can happen?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It can be true, it can be another lie.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said, I'm going.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I cannot take it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The shoes-- I was walking barefoot in mud, in rain.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It began to snow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was December, it was dreadful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And another woman from my hometown said, I'll go, too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, we went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They picked about 150 women, end of December.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And indeed, clearly, the train was not blown up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We ended up in a labor camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
